{"tid":1166834,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"Christopher Nolan 諜戰主題新戲 <Tenet> 卡士陣容公佈","createTime":"2019-05-22T16:32:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-28T13:42:49.000Z","uid":36509,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"35eaf00d85ab23346004d73757533df4578b35cf","tid":1166834,"uid":36509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T16:32:03.000Z","msg":"Aaron Taylor-Johnson and Kenneth Branagh will appear in Christopher Nolan&rsquo;s upcoming film, &ldquo;Tenet.&rdquo; Cl&eacute;mence Po&eacute;sy, Dimple Kapadia, Michael Caine are also joining the cast that includes John David Washington, Elizabeth Debicki, and Robert Pattinson<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">&ldquo;Tenet,&rdquo; which is being filmed on location across seven countries, is an action epic evolving from the world of international espionage.</span></strong><br />\n<br />\nNolan is directing from his own original screenplay and will use a mix of Imax and 70mm film to bring the story to the big screen.<br />\n<br />\nNolan and his wife, Emma Thomas are producing the movie, while Thomas Hayslip is serving as executive producer.<br />\n<br />\nWarner Bros. Pictures is distributing &ldquo;Tenet&rdquo; worldwide. It is scheduled to hit theaters on <span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>July 17, 2020.</strong></span><br />\n<br />\nMore:<br />\n<a href=\"https://variety.com/2019/film/news/christopher-nolan-tenet-aaron-taylor-johnson-kenneth-branagh-1203223474/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F2019%2Ffilm%2Fnews%2Fchristopher-nolan-tenet-aaron-taylor-johnson-kenneth-branagh-1203223474%2F&d=cCjVArjaL4JVgeQxTlbTS%2Fno2Xhlbsa%2F7jwkLKy9%2F%2FE%3D&h=81a2122e\" target=\"_blank\">https://variety.com/2019/film/news/christopher-nolan-tenet-aaron-taylor-johnson-kenneth-branagh-1203223474/</a>"},{"pid":"914710f0a1cf241014de50f375ecfc8445c03fb6","tid":1166834,"uid":2054,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"20